{
  "id": "rules_glossary/a/attach",
  "lookup_group": "rules_glossary",
  "lookup_id": "attach",
  "title": "Attach",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Some cards instruct you to"
        },
        {
          "type": "b",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "attach"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "them to other cards. When you do, place the attached card underneath the card to which it is attached with a bit poking out to remind you that it\u2019s there."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Faceup attached cards are considered to be \u201c"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "in play"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/i/in_play",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/I/in_play"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ",\u201d while"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "facedown"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/f/facedown_cards",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/F/facedown_cards"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "attached cards are not."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "There is no limit to the number of cards that can be attached to a card."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When a card is attached"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "facedown"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/f/facedown_cards",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/F/facedown_cards"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "discard"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/d/discard",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/D/discard"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "any tokens from it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When a card leaves play, any cards attached to it are"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "discarded"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/d/discard",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/D/discard"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Some cards can attach to your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "role"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/role",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/role"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". You can still"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "interact"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/i/interact",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/I/interact"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "with these cards."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Resolve challenge effects on cards attached to your role as if they were"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "within reach"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/w/within_reach",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/W/within_reach"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "When you"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "interact"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/i/interact",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/I/interact"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "with other cards"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "in play"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/i/in_play",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/I/in_play"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", cards attached to your"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "role"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/role",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/role"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "always count as being between you and that card. That is, a"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "ready"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/ready",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/ready"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "card attached to your role will"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "fatigue"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/f/fatigue",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/F/fatigue"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "you when you"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "interact"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/i/interact",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/I/interact"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "with another card in play."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "On rare occasions, a card can become attached to a card that is itself attached to another card. There is no limit to the amount of cards that can be attached in this way."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "img",
      "items": []
    },
    {
      "type": "h6",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Camoveave Cloak with Universal Power Cells attached"
        },
        {
